-- Bear Stearns names head of investment strategy
-- 
-- Thu Oct 11, 2007 11:33am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/10/11/us-bearstearns-golub-idUSWNAS610220071011

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Bear Stearns Cos Inc BSC.N said on Thursday Jonathan Golub, previously U.S. equity strategist at JP Morgan Asset Management, has joined the firm as senior managing director and chief investment strategist. 

 Golub, who has 20 years of investment industry experience, is based in New York, the company said in a statement. (Reporting by  Lilla Zuill )